channel.description:
[center][img]http://i.imgur.com/dQtTHCP.png[/img][/center]
[center][size=18pt]www.divinationofgods.com[/size][/center] [center][size=14pt]Client (Cache auto downloads)[/size][/center] [center][size=14pt]To Download Client, go to website and click Menu option in top left![/size][/center] [center][youtube]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p8GvzFTwTvg[/youtube][/center] [center][size=14pt]Notices: No longer in beta. Full game uploaded to site, no Hamachi.[/size][/center] [center][size=24pt]LOTS OF UPDATES! NEW FORUMS! IRON MAN MODE!!![/size][/center] [center][size=18pt]Welcome to Divination of Gods, Let me show you around[/size][/center] [center][size=18pt]NEW UPDATES: NEW WEBSITE NEW FORUMS HIGHSCORES NEW WEAPONS NEW ARMORS NEW RARES NEW MONSTERS AND MORE! 12/9/2014 NEW GOD SYSTEM *CHOOSE YOUR GOD* NEW NEW HOME NEW POINT SYSTEM WORKING ON CUSTOM HOMES FOR EACH GOD FACTION OPENING NEW QUEST LINE LIKE NOTHING YOUVE SEEN BEFORE! 12/13/2014[/size][/center] [center][img]http://i.imgur.com/mQZRLfH.png[/img][/center]
[center][size=18pt]Firstly... Let us start out by saying.. Everyone seems to ask what makes us different from the rest. Well ask our community? We are constantly working on new updates to excel above the rest! At this very moment our owner Mod Jesse is working hard on making something NO OTHER SERVER HAS! We are coming up with new pets.. for everyone's favorite skill, Slayer! Here is a sneak peak into some of the monster's we're coming out with as pets![/size][/center] [center][size=14pt]Fast growing![/size][/center] [center][img]http://i.imgur.com/xIQng1r.jpg[/img][/center] [center][img]http://i.imgur.com/kWp91A4.png[/img][/center] [center][img]http://i.imgur.com/r5kZnGT.png[/img][/center] [center]We have curses[/center] [center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/h1uScUV.png[/img][/center]
[center]And Tormented Demons[/center] [center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/p8lPwIi.png[/img][/center]
[center]As well as other bosses[/center] [center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/ikmpaYe.png[/img][/center]
[center]Points system[/center] [center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/L4d1OLK.png[/img][/center] [center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/JD2dW1U.png[/img][/center] [center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/h1mDSRE.png[/img][/center]
[center]Godwars[/center] [center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/9TtRfTl.png[/img][/center]
[center]Nex[/center] [center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/RD0v89g.png[/img][/center]
[center][size=18pt]WE HAVE SO MUCH MORE, INCLUDING FULL HD FULL SCREEN OPTION[/size][/center] [center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/DQdJ6UT.png[/img][/center] [center][size=24pt]To sumarize, We have a great economy and a great playing experience, We listen to our community and poll updates we think might need poled. We also are very kind and you'll never find a rude staff member. If you do I can assure you they won't be there long. We love having players on and do this simply for the players. Why else would we spend hours of our time thinking of updates to better the playing experience? :) We sincerely hope to see you soon![/size][/center]
[size=18pt][center]NO LONGER USING HAMACHI, VPS hosted 24/7![/center][/size]
